VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT LdapConnection\s*\(|new\s+LdapConnection
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:Request\.|QueryString|Form|userInput|\+ && MISSING:EscapeLdapFilter|AntiXss\.LdapFilterEncode
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects LdapConnection usage in .NET where search queries may use unvalidated user input.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for LDAP Injection: LdapConnection Bind or Search.
